entries.femaleVariant: Hmmm-hmmm, hmmm-hmmm…
Great.
Great, signal's clear. Just need your help with a few basic checks.
Next up – sound check.
I know that song.
Don't know the title. Can hum it back, though.
Hey, I know that! Etta Sorrentino – "Only You."
No idea what the song is, but I heard it. Uh, goes something like…
entries.maleVariant: No idea what the song is... but I heard it. Goes something like…

entries.femaleVariant: First up – motion sensors and scrollin'.
Great, motion calibrated. Now swim hither?
entries.maleVariant: Great, motion calibrated. Back my way now, V.

entries.femaleVariant: Never did go in for sentimental stuff... Got stuck in my head lately, though, that one.
All right, we're all tuned and synced.
Incredible.
Had no idea there were buildings down here.
You wanna explore that?
That's-- That's incredible... What is it?
Had no idea... If you'd said we'd see a sunken town…
Impressive, huh?
Like it?
Enjoying the view?
Swim over here an' look straight at me, will ya?
Hmmm-hmmm, hmmm-hmmm…
Our very own Atlantis.
Dunno. Sure as hell never seen anything like it, can tell you that.
All right, that oughta do it.
Didn't fuck up a thing.
Need to calibrate our gear.
Circle around me, swim.
But... I hear you just fine.
Need a wider range. Levels can't be short of perfect.
Yep, view's preem.
Um, sorry.
Hang on, you can see what I see?
Visual sensors're gettin' stimmed right now, can't be denied.
Oh, uff... sorry.
Whoa. Y-You see what I see, like, in real-time?
entries.maleVariant: Whoa. You see what I see? In real-time? Like, what I'm lookin' at?

entries.femaleVariant: Hahaha... Don't get excited. Oxygen supply's limited.
entries.maleVariant: I'm gonna pretend I didn't hear that.

entries.femaleVariant: Whaaat? Don't be.
entries.maleVariant: Don't lemme catch you at it again.

entries.femaleVariant: Oh, yeah. I see everything.
entries.maleVariant: Mhm. And I gotta say it's pretty fucking weird.

entries.femaleVariant: To think I never realized how fit you were.
Right. We were gonna take in our surroundings.
entries.maleVariant: Right. We were, uh, gonna take in our surroundings.

entries.femaleVariant: Could prove more difficult than we thought...
That proves it – I officially suck. Probably fucked up the settings…
Whatever you wanna do, Judy. Guess I'm with you.
Ahh! Too loud!
Hang on, that's prolly too loud. Should be OK... now.
And now? Better?
Lots, thanks.
Read me?
Didn't fuck anything up.
Whoa! OK... Works better than I thought. Gonna dial it down a bit.
Whoa! Oww!
I'm 'onna hum a song, you gimme the title.
Got some connection to this place?
You wanna explore all that?
Used to be called Laguna Bend. Just fifteen years ago, people still lived here.
Got some connection to this place, right?
What happened here? Why'd it get flooded?
[Let go] Let's get moving.
Sounds nova. Let's do this.
Yeah... I remember.
What happened here?
Why are you showing me this?
Yeah... I remember.
Why are you showing me this?
This'll be perfect? For what, exactly?
Why's this stand to be perfect?
'Cause someone stood to profit.
NC Dam Ltd. made plans to build a dam. People protested, and... the rest is history.
entries.maleVariant: NC Dam Ltd. made plans to build a dam. People protested, and the rest is history.

entries.femaleVariant: You got it. Grew up here.
Haven't been back since Laguna Bend was wiped off the map.
Ready to wrestle with the demons of my past?
It's important to me.
entries.maleVariant: Wanna get the right emotional reactions.

entries.femaleVariant: Got a feeling this'll be perfect for my experiment.
Hopin' you'll be able to pick up all the unfiltered mess of emotions this place brings out in me.
[Grab] Down we go!
Down we go!
Not me. I want you to explore it.
Houses, playgrounds – all flooded.
Now grab this and hold on tight.
Like it or not, you'll react to those feelings. That's what I wanna capture.
All right, that oughta do it. We are now…
Synced.
What now?
Prepare to have your mind blown. Wait for it...
And you've got talent, girl.
Don't dive down alone. Wetsuit won't stand the pressure.
V, this isn't a joke! You go down there alone, the pressure'll kill you!
Hear you just fine.
